cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.CC, cs.PL

This paper deals with databases and their repairs, which falls under the category of cs.DB (Databases). It also uses answer-set programs, which are a type of logic programming, falling under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses reasoning and computation, which could fall under cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity). Finally, the paper presents repair programs, which are a type of programming language, falling under cs.PL (Programming Languages).
